statements: SELECT lead_id, lead_name, lead_score, lead_status FROM LeadScoringModels;
SELECT lead_name, lead_status, lead_score FROM LeadScoringModels;
SELECT lead_name, lead_score FROM LeadScoringModels WHERE lead_score > 70;
SELECT * FROM LeadScoringModels WHERE lead_status = 'Active';
SELECT lead_id, lead_name FROM LeadScoringModels ORDER BY lead_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM LeadScoringModels WHERE lead_score > 70 ORDER BY lead_name DESC;
SELECT lead_name, lead_score FROM LeadScoringModels WHERE lead_status = 'Qualified' ORDER BY lead_score DESC;
SELECT lead_id, lead_name, lead_status FROM LeadScoringModels WHERE lead_id IN (1001, 1003, 1005);
SELECT * FROM LeadScoringModels WHERE lead_score BETWEEN 50 AND 80 ORDER BY lead_id;
SELECT COUNT(lead_id) AS total_leads, AVG(lead_score) AS avg_score FROM LeadScoringModels WHERE lead_status = 'Converted';
SELECT * FROM leads;
SELECT lead_name, lead_email FROM leads ORDER BY lead_name DESC;
SELECT lead_id, lead_name FROM leads WHERE lead_score > 50;
SELECT * FROM leads WHERE lead_score BETWEEN 30 AND 70 ORDER BY lead_score DESC;
SELECT lead_id, lead_email, lead_score FROM leads WHERE lead_email LIKE '%@example.com';
SELECT * FROM leads WHERE lead_score > 80 ORDER BY lead_name DESC;
SELECT lead_name, lead_email FROM leads WHERE lead_score BETWEEN 60 AND 80 ORDER BY lead_score DESC, lead_name ASC;
SELECT lead_name, score_value, score_date FROM leads JOIN lead_scores ON leads.lead_id = lead_scores.lead_id WHERE score_value < 50 ORDER BY score_date DESC;
SELECT lead_email, score_value FROM leads JOIN lead_scores ON leads.lead_id = lead_scores.lead_id WHERE lead_score IS NULL ORDER BY lead_email ASC;
SELECT lead_name, lead_email, score_date FROM leads JOIN lead_scores ON leads.lead_id = lead_scores.lead_id WHERE score_value >= 70 ORDER BY score_date ASC, lead_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM Lead;
SELECT lead_name, lead_score FROM Lead ORDER BY lead_score DESC;
SELECT lead_id, lead_stage FROM Lead WHERE lead_stage = 'Prospect';
SELECT activity_id, lead_id, activity_type, activity_date FROM LeadActivity WHERE lead_id = 1001;
SELECT lead_id, interaction_type, interaction_result FROM LeadInteraction ORDER BY interaction_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM Lead;
SELECT lead_name, lead_score, lead_source FROM Lead WHERE lead_score > 80;
SELECT lead_name, lead_stage, interaction_date FROM Lead INNER JOIN LeadInteraction ON Lead.lead_id = LeadInteraction.lead_id WHERE LeadInteraction.interaction_result = 'Positive';
SELECT lead_name, activity_date, activity_description FROM Lead INNER JOIN LeadActivity ON Lead.lead_id = LeadActivity.lead_id WHERE LeadActivity.activity_type = 'Meeting';

SELECT lead_name, lead_score, lead_stage, interaction_date, interaction_result FROM Lead INNER JOIN LeadInteraction ON Lead.lead_id = LeadInteraction.lead_id WHERE lead_score < 50 AND interaction_result = 'Neutral' ORDER BY interaction_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM leads;
SELECT lead_name, lead_email, lead_score FROM leads ORDER BY lead_score DESC;
SELECT lead_id, lead_name FROM leads WHERE lead_score > 80;
SELECT * FROM lead_activities WHERE activity_type = 'Email' AND activity_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT lead_id, MAX(lead_score) AS highest_score FROM lead_scores GROUP BY lead_id;
SELECT lead_name, lead_email FROM leads;
SELECT * FROM leads WHERE lead_score > 80;
SELECT lead_id, MAX(lead_score) AS highest_score FROM lead_scores GROUP BY lead_id;
SELECT leads.lead_name, lead_activities.activity_type, lead_activities.activity_date FROM leads JOIN lead_activities ON leads.lead_id = lead_activities.lead_id;
SELECT lead_name, nurturing_date, nurturing_description FROM leads INNER JOIN lead_nurturing ON leads.lead_id = lead_nurturing.lead_id WHERE nurturing_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM lead_data;
SELECT lead_name, lead_email, lead_score FROM lead_data;
SELECT lead_id, lead_name, lead_status FROM lead_data ORDER BY lead_id DESC;
SELECT lead_id, lead_email FROM lead_data WHERE lead_score > 50;
SELECT COUNT(lead_id) AS total_leads FROM lead_data;
SELECT lead_name, lead_email FROM lead_data WHERE lead_score > 80 ORDER BY lead_name ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT * FROM lead_interaction WHERE interaction_date >= '2022-01-01' AND interaction_type = 'Meeting' ORDER BY interaction_date DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT lead_id, lead_name, lead_email, lead_score FROM lead_data WHERE lead_status = 'Active' ORDER BY lead_score DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT l.lead_id, l.lead_name, ls.source_type FROM lead_data l JOIN lead_source ls ON l.lead_id = ls.source_id WHERE ls.source_name = 'Webinar' ORDER BY l.lead_name ASC LIMIT 5

SELECT lp.lead_id, lp.priority_level, lp.priority_status, ln.nurture_date FROM lead_priority lp JOIN lead_nurture ln ON lp.lead_id = ln.lead_id WHERE lp.priority_level > 2 ORDER BY ln.nurture_date DESC LIMIT 5
